這是范崔普家庭
This will be the last opportunity the von Trapps will have...

1810
02:39:14,721 --> 02:39:17,121
最後一次合唱 此後，大概不會再有機會了
...of singing together for a long, long time.

1811
02:39:18,191 --> 02:39:22,184
