我們先公佈第三名
We will start with the award for third prize.

1841
02:42:11,698 --> 02:42:14,030
我有幸向你們宣佈裁判決定
For this honor, the judges have named...

1842
02:42:14,301 --> 02:42:18,897
第三名的得主 是聖雅嘉佛合唱團的第一獨唱者
...the first soloist of the choir of St. Agatha's Church in Murback.

1843
02:42:19,172 --> 02:42:21,402
史萊瓦格小姐
Fraulein Schweiger.

1844
02:42:58,345 --> 02:43:02,281
第二名是圖比萊撒四重唱
Second prize to The Toby Reiser Quintet.

1845
02:43:30,243 --> 02:43:34,407
第一名，奧地利的最高榮譽獎…
And the first prize, the highest honor in all Austria...

1846
02:43:34,647 --> 02:43:37,741
范崔普家庭歌詠團
...the von Trapp Family Singers.

1847
02:43:50,130 --> 02:43:51,791
范崔普家庭
The family von Trapp.

1848
02:44:06,413 --> 02:44:07,471
他們走了
They're gone!

1849
