You two, cover the corridor.

1859
02:45:40,039 --> 02:45:43,600
院長，沒想到連累了修道院
Reverend Mother, we didn't realize we put the abbey in this danger.

1860
02:45:43,877 --> 02:45:46,402
不，?莉亞，你們來是對的
No, Maria, it was right for you to come here.

1861
02:45:46,613 --> 02:45:48,513
我們想借用你們的車
We thought we might borrow your car.

1862
02:45:48,715 --> 02:45:50,615
你們用不著車了
I'm afraid our car will do you no good now.

1863
02:45:51,217 --> 02:45:52,878
我聽無線電說
I've been listening to the wires.

1864
02:45:53,086 --> 02:45:55,611
邊界被封鎖了
The borders have just been closed.

1865
02:46:01,461 --> 02:46:03,759
好吧，邊界被封鎖了
All right, if the borders are closed...

1866
02:46:05,064 --> 02:46:08,363
那麼我們開車到山裡 再徒步過去
...then we'll drive up into the hills and go over the mountains on foot.

1867
02:46:08,968 --> 02:46:10,959
-和小孩們？ -我們會幫他們的
- The children... - We'll help them.

1868
02:46:11,237 --> 02:46:13,398
爸爸，我們不需要幫助
We can do it without help, Father.

1869
02:46:14,440 --> 02:46:15,805
?莉亞
Maria.

1870
02:46:16,543 --> 02:46:19,137
你不會孤獨無助的，記住
You will not be alone. Remember:

1871
02:46:19,379 --> 02:46:22,473
“我要向山舉目 我的幫助從何而來”
"I will lift up mine eyes unto the hills from whence cometh my help."

1872
02:46:23,449 --> 02:46:24,541
是的，院長
Yes, Mother.

1873
02:46:25,919 --> 02:46:28,080
-我好害怕 -我也是
- I'm scared. - Me too.

1874
02:46:40,166 --> 02:46:41,326
願主與你同在
God be with you.

1875
02:46:48,274 --> 02:46:49,832
-媽 -是的？
- Mother. - Yes?

1876
02:46:50,076 --> 02:46:53,273
如我們唱“心愛的事物” 會有幫助嗎？
Would it help if we sang about our favorite things?

1877
02:46:53,513 --> 02:46:56,505
不，親愛的 這是唯一幫不上忙的一次
No, darling. This is one time it would not help.

1878
02:46:56,783 --> 02:46:59,980
你必須很安靜，緊抱著我
You must be very quiet. Hold tight to me.

1879
02:49:14,654 --> 02:49:15,882
我們到屋頂看看
Let's try the roof.

1880
02:50:12,145 --> 02:50:14,375
勞夫，求求你
Rolfe, please.

1881
02:50:19,485 --> 02:50:20,975
不要，等一下
No, wait.

1882
02:50:30,797 --> 02:50:32,128
?莉亞
Maria.

1883
02:50:33,199 --> 02:50:34,632
孩子們
Children.

1884
02:50:38,671 --> 02:50:41,697
我們要的只是你
It's you we want, not them.

1885
02:50:42,074 --> 02:50:43,803
把那個放下
Put that down.

1886
02:50:44,877 --> 02:50:48,176
不准動，否則我就開槍
Not another move, or I'll shoot.

1887
02:50:49,882 --> 02:50:51,907
你只是個孩子
You're only a boy.

1888
02:50:54,921 --> 02:50:58,584
-你並不是他們的人 -站在原地
- You don't really belong to them. - Stay where you are.

1889
02:51:00,359 --> 02:51:02,350
跟我們逃吧
Come away with us.

1890
02:51:03,596 --> 02:51:04,756
現在還來得及
Before it's too late.

1891
02:51:05,364 --> 02:51:07,696
你再行一步，我就殺了你
Not another step. I'll kill you.

1892
02:51:10,002 --> 02:51:13,335
-把槍給我，勞夫 -你有沒有聽到？
- You give that to me, Rolfe. - Did you hear me?

1893
02:51:14,340 --> 02:51:15,898
我會殺了你
I'll kill you.

1894
02:51:17,777 --> 02:51:19,244
勞夫
Rolfe.

1895
02:51:37,630 --> 02:51:38,961
你永遠不會跟他們一樣
You'll never be one of them.

1896
02:51:41,734 --> 02:51:43,429
中尉
Lieutenant!

1897
02:51:43,703 --> 02:51:44,829
他們在這裡
They're here!

1898
02:51:45,037 --> 02:51:46,595
他們在這裡，中尉
They're here, lieutenant!

1899
02:52:27,914 --> 02:52:29,575
院長
Reverend Mother.

1900
02:52:30,850 --> 02:52:32,681
我有罪
I have sinned.

1901
02:52:33,853 --> 02:52:36,014
院長，我也是
I too, Reverend Mother.

1902
02:52:37,657 --> 02:52:39,989
孩子們，是什麼罪？
What is this sin, my children?


